Package: smmartbodymap
Type: Package
Title: Plot Cancer Lesions on an Anatomical Map
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("Lauren", "Murray", email = "smmartbodymap@laurenmurray.me",
  role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0001-6876-2760"))
Description: smmartbodymap formats and plots datasets of cancer lesions on an 
    anatomical map. The resulting plot displays lesion locations over time,
    plotted based on their ICD-O-3 morphological location. Inspired by the 
    BodyMapR package.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: 
    R (>= 2.10)
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
